# Directory Restructuring - Walkthrough

**Date:** February 2, 2026

## Summary

Successfully refactored the project directory structure from a cluttered 36-item root to a clean 9-item professional layout.

---

## Before/After Comparison

### Before (Cluttered)
```
Root: 27 files + 9 directories = 36 items

Problems:
- 8 markdown docs scattered at root
- 6 shell scripts at root
- 7 duplicate zip files (~530MB)
- Confusing names (ldm_test, testbackend)
```

### After (Clean)
```
Root: 3 files + 6 directories = 9 items

ldm-college-erp/
├── frontend/     ← React app (was ldm_test)
├── api/          ← PHP backend
├── gibbon/       ← ERP core (was testbackend)
├── database/     ← SQL files organized
├── scripts/      ← All scripts categorized
├── docs/         ← All documentation
├── archives/     ← Old deployments
├── public/       ← Static assets
├── README.md     ← New project readme
├── router.php    ← PHP routing
└── .user.ini     ← PHP config
```

---

## Changes Made

### Phase 1: Created Directory Structure
Created organized subdirectories:
- `docs/{setup,api,security,reports}`
- `database/{schema,migrations,backups}`
- `scripts/{deploy,database,testing,backup}`
- `archives/`

### Phase 2: Moved Documentation (8 files)
| File | New Location |
|------|--------------|
| LOCAL_SETUP.md | docs/setup/ |
| BACKUP_SETUP_GUIDE.md | docs/setup/ |
| DOCUMENTATION.md | docs/api/ |
| SECURITY_STEP1_VERIFICATION.md | docs/security/ |
| FINAL_COMPLETION_REPORT.md | docs/reports/ |
| PRIORITY1_COMPLETION_REPORT.md | docs/reports/ |
| STEP2_COMPLETION_SUMMARY.md | docs/reports/ |
| PROJECT_NOTES.md | docs/reports/ |

### Phase 3: Organized Database Files
| File | New Location |
|------|--------------|
| create_tables.sql | database/schema/ |
| audit_and_permissions.sql | database/schema/ |
| create_admin_user.sql | database/migrations/ |
| ldm_production_20260201.sql.gz | database/backups/ |
| optimize_database.sql | database/migrations/ |

### Phase 4: Organized Scripts (12 files)
- Deploy scripts → `scripts/deploy/`
- Database scripts → `scripts/database/`
- Testing scripts → `scripts/testing/`
- Backup scripts → `scripts/backup/`

### Phase 5: Archived Duplicates (~530MB)
Moved to `archives/`:
- 7 zip files (deployment packages)
- 2 duplicate directories (deploy_package, final_deploy_v2)

### Phase 6: Renamed Directories
| Old Name | New Name | Reason |
|----------|----------|--------|
| ldm_test | frontend | Clearer purpose |
| testbackend | gibbon | Actual content |
| frontend_integration | (deleted) | Unused files |

### Phase 7: Created README.md
New comprehensive project README with:
- Directory structure overview
- Quick start guide
- Documentation links
- Tech stack summary

